snippet.title: Kinect Star Wars Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Star Wars like never before...using your whole body and without a controller.  Feel the force as you become a Jedi, drive a Podracer, pilot a starfighter, and wreak havoc as a Rancor monster in Kinect Star Wars!  

ESRB Rating: TEEN
